README

  cnc (Client Network Checker) is a tool to gather clients' network stats
  when they are experiencing issues such as slow downloads. The information
  this tool gathers will help us troubleshooting what is causing clients'
  issues.

INFORMATION

  This tool will collect the following information of client's machine:
    + IP/ISP
    + OS (such as machine name, OS/kernel version)
    + CPU (how many are installed)
    + Memory (total, free, used for physical and virtual)

TEST

  This tool will run the following network tests:
    + Ping
    + Trace
    + Download Speed
